column5: Mr. Mercer, in all his effeminate glory took his show to algonquin park to do some aerial surveys, and bear tagging.  Hilarity ensues!
Dude! He went skinny dipping with a failed politician. Anyone worth watching would have at least lined up a hot female pol. - Are there any of those?  JF
belinda stronach was kind of foxy, although she only gets naked with hockey tough guys...

What do you call a failed politician, The one that has won a majority and is still elected and drawing a wage or the one that has never won a majority and still holds his job because he got rid of anybody in his party smart enough to take it away from him.  I think Bob's made a pretty good living as a politician.
he made a good living  and we are still paying for the stupid spending he did  and lets not forget Rae Days............  he had great ideas but not a clue on how to pay for his programs
I would have been much more interested in this thread if Rick's name was replaced with Dave's.
but dave isn't girly enough to make it funny!
